Farinelli;;1994;;R;;Biography,Drama,Music;;6.8;;Gérard Corbiau;;Stefano Dionisi,Enrico Lo Verso,Elsa Zylberstein,Caroline Cellier,Marianne Basler,Jacques Boudet,Graham Valentine,Pier Paolo Capponi,Renaud du Peloux de Saint Romain,Delphine Zentout,Omero Antonutti,Jeroen Krabbé,Richard Reeves,Jonathan Fox,Jo Betzing,Karl-Heinz Dickmann,Stefan Mazel,Wolfgang Grindemann;;Farinelli is the artistic name of Carlo Broschi, a young singer in Handel's time. He was castrated in his childhood in order to preserve his voice. During his life he becomes a very famous opera singer, managed by his mediocre brother (Riccardo).;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0109771/